TextBlock.Text: BABYASS: Oh my god that took a lot of work... But we're here. The sun of this system is red and bright, and this moon is drenched.
BITCHASS: Come on Babyass, you know why we're here. Let's get moving!
KICKASS: Haha! I found the engraving first- and oop-
KICKASS: The engraving appears to be the start of a new coordinate. It goes from top right to bottom left, and oddly enough, to the bottom right.
BABYASS: Gah... This is getting boring.
BITCHASS: Shut up, Babyass. No wonder you were named that. You are such a child.
KICKASS: Alright, we all know how this goes. The secondary engraving is of that planet filled with the symbol that looks like A.
